name: The New Normal
description:
"The New Normal" a song by artist Christina LaRocca. 

This is my very first NFT. A full mastered song along with 3D artwork. 

Music & Lyrics by Christina LaRocca
Production & Musical Arrangements by Gene Micofsky
Lyrics on Robot Outro by Jacob Voelzke
Artwork by Christina LaRocca

The new normal feels pretty strange
They keep trying to farm inside my brain
And mine me like a crystal cave
Steal my thoughts, my words, hit save
Terms & conditions
They may apply 
I check the box - I don’t ask why
My phone records every word I say
Even though I said “it’s not okay”

Its the new
The new
The new 
It’s the new normal
The new
The new 
It’s the new normal


The new normal keeps on calling me
Excuse me please tell me what this is regarding
There’s nothing social ‘bout my anxiety
Signing off is how I work on my sobriety
They’re living like parasites up in your mind
Auctioning everything they find
Money is the lover they long to embrace
Even if they destroy the whole human race

Its the new
The new
The new 
It’s the new normal
The new
The new 
It’s the new normal

They know where you sleep
They know what you eat 
They know who you’re creepin’ with
They know about you
What you like to do 
And they’re sellin’ you, 
Sellin’ you
Sellin’ you….

Its the new
The new
The new 
It’s the new normal
The new
The new 
It’s the new normal


This is just a taste of what’s to come
This is just a waste until it’s done
And are you okay with what you’ve become?
Do you feel a void for what’s undone?

Think of all the times you’ve kept inside
All the changes, turned pages, and paradigms
But i don’t bend to the winds of one
And i don’t mourn the setting sun

I ride waves that pull the moon
Rise & fade like fog & gloom
And when the tides of time renew
We’ll all have left our old cocoons

It’s the new normal
The new
The new 
It’s the new normal

Upon purchasing, please send me a DM on twitter, and I will send you the full HD version if you'd like it. 

thank you.
